WEBVTT

00:05.770 --> 00:10.264
Captions made possible by
HOME BOX OFFICE, INC.

01:43.570 --> 01:45.595
OKAY, SWEETHEART,
IT'S TIME TO SAY GOODBYE.

01:45.630 --> 01:46.767
I DON'T WANT TO.

01:46.800 --> 01:47.892
BUT WE HAVE TO.

01:47.940 --> 01:49.532
GOD HAS OTHER
PLANS FOR HER.

01:49.570 --> 01:51.709
I'LL MISS YOU, BIRDIE.

01:51.740 --> 01:53.401
I KNOW, SWEETH EART.

01:53.440 --> 01:55.704
BUT BY RESCUING HER
AND NURSING HER BACK TO HEALTH

01:55.740 --> 01:57.708
AND NOW
SETTING HER FREE,

01:57.750 --> 01:59.809
WE ARE DOING
A GOOD DEED.

01:59.850 --> 02:01.511
GOOD DEED !

02:01.550 --> 02:04.439
WHEN WE DO SOMETHING KIND,
EVEN FOR A LITTLE LOST BIRD,

02:04.490 --> 02:06.412
WE GIVE A GIFT

02:06.460 --> 02:08.451
THAT RESONATES
THROUGHOUT ALL HUMANITY.

02:08.490 --> 02:10.151
HUMANITY !

02:10.190 --> 02:11.384
SAY BYE BYE.

02:11.430 --> 02:12.499
BYE BYE.

02:12.530 --> 02:14.395
BE FREE,
LITTLE LOST BIRD.

02:14.430 --> 02:15.226
BE FREE.

02:18.800 --> 02:21.769
"NO, FUCK YOU,
MOTHERFUCKER !"

02:23.540 --> 02:24.666
NO, FUCK YOU.

02:24.710 --> 02:27.372
YOU'RE A
MOTHERFUCKER !

02:28.510 --> 02:30.899
OH, FUCK ME.

02:34.750 --> 02:36.911
IT'S BROKEN !

02:36.950 --> 02:39.180
BIRD CRAPPED
ON MY HAT.

02:39.220 --> 02:40.482
I JUST NEED
TO WASH IT.

02:40.520 --> 02:41.657
ALRIGHT.

02:41.690 --> 02:42.952
JUST USE THE SINK.

02:42.990 --> 02:44.355
TOILET BROKEN.

02:44.390 --> 02:45.687
AND HURRY UP.

02:45.730 --> 02:46.719
I'M GOING TO CLOSE.

02:48.500 --> 02:53.199
FUCK YOU, MOTHERFUCKER,
FUCK YOU, MOTHERFUCKER.

02:53.240 --> 02:54.730
FUCK YOU,
MOTHERFUCKER.

02:54.770 --> 02:57.637
FUCK YOU,
MOTHERFUCKER.

02:57.670 --> 03:02.300
FUCK YOU,
MOTHERFUCKER.

03:03.780 --> 03:04.940
( toilet flushing )

03:04.980 --> 03:07.278
I TOLD YOU
IT WAS BROKEN !

03:07.320 --> 03:09.311
FUCK YOU,
MOTHERFUCKER !

03:11.590 --> 03:13.353
EXCELLENT.

03:13.390 --> 03:14.755
FUCK A-FEE YOU.

03:14.790 --> 03:17.918
( speaking Armenian )

03:17.960 --> 03:19.496
( phone ringing )

03:22.730 --> 03:25.665
HELLO ?

03:25.700 --> 03:27.759
( speaking Armenian )

03:34.640 --> 03:37.905
( static on phone )

04:02.540 --> 04:03.507
ANAHID ?

04:05.670 --> 04:07.672
ANAHID ?

04:07.710 --> 04:10.304
HELLO, HELLO ?

05:04.800 --> 05:06.859
(Uw)
SO, WHAT ARE YOU SAYING,
YOU WANT TO LEAVE ?

05:06.900 --> 05:07.992
( Nate )
LEAVE ?

05:08.040 --> 05:09.735
OH NO, I WOULD
HAVE TO LEAVE,

05:09.770 --> 05:11.362
BECAUSE I MOVED MY WHOLE FUCKING
LIFE TO THIS SHITHOLE CITY.

05:11.410 --> 05:13.002
NOT FOR ME,
YOU DIDN'T !

05:13.040 --> 05:14.007
SO, YOU WANT
TO SPLIT UP ?

05:14.040 --> 05:14.972
MAYBE, YEAH.

05:38.000 --> 05:43.108
( baby crying )

05:47.840 --> 05:50.547
WHO IN THE WORLD WOULD JUST
LEAVE A CHILD ALONE LIKE THAT ?

05:50.580 --> 05:52.047
OH, DON'T BE
TOO HARD ON HIM.

05:52.080 --> 05:53.547
HE'S NOT HIMSELF
RIGHT NOW.

05:53.580 --> 05:55.946
BESIDES, MAYA IS
FAR FROM ALONE,

05:55.980 --> 05:57.743
AREN'T YOU,
LI'I'I'LE LADY ?

05:57.790 --> 05:59.587
GO TO GRANDMA.

05:59.620 --> 06:02.418
THERE YOU GO.

06:18.470 --> 06:21.405
SO, WHAT IS NATE LIKE
A TOTAL ALKIE NOW ?

06:21.440 --> 06:22.600
I MEAN, SHOULD WE
DO SOMETHING ?

06:22.650 --> 06:24.106
HE'S JUST
NUMBING THE PAIN.

06:24.150 --> 06:25.447
HE HAS TO.

06:25.480 --> 06:27.812
SOMETIMES HE GOES
OUTSIDE TO SMOKE,

06:27.850 --> 06:29.613
AND HE PACES
UNDERNEATH MY WINDOW.

06:29.650 --> 06:31.413
HE TALKS TO HIMSELF.

06:31.450 --> 06:32.610
I KNOW.

06:32.660 --> 06:35.515
SERIOUSLY, LIKE
WHOLE CONVERSATIONS.

06:42.870 --> 06:45.020
WHY IS EVERYONE
IN MY HOUSE ?

06:45.070 --> 06:47.459
MAYA WAS CRYING HER
LITTLE HEART OUT.

06:47.500 --> 06:49.502
WHERE IN THE WORLD WOULD YOU GO
AT 4:30 IN THE MORNING ?

06:49.540 --> 06:50.939
I WAS HAVING
A CIGARETTE.

06:50.970 --> 06:52.631
IN POMONA ?

06:52.680 --> 06:54.705
WE HEARD HER CRYING
ALL THE WAY IN THE HOUSE.

06:54.740 --> 06:55.934
ALL OF US,
POOR THING.

06:55.980 --> 06:57.470
POOR LITTLE BABY.

06:57.510 --> 06:59.046
YOU THOUGHT
NO ONE LOVED YOU.

06:59.080 --> 07:02.481
MOM, I CAN TAKE HER.

07:08.490 --> 07:09.923
WHERE'S HER BLANKY ?

07:09.960 --> 07:12.690
OH, I HAVE IT.

07:12.730 --> 07:14.095
ARE YOU
LIVING HERE NOW ?

07:14.130 --> 07:15.495
NATE !

07:19.770 --> 07:21.032
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

07:21.070 --> 07:22.935
I'M GOING TO MAKE
A BIG POT OF COFFEE,

07:22.970 --> 07:25.609
AND THEN YOUR MOTHER AND I
WOULD LIKE TO TALK TO YOU GUYS.

07:25.640 --> 07:29.428
IN THE KITCHEN,
IN SAY ABOUT 10 MINUTES ?

07:39.790 --> 07:40.882
YOU'RE GETTING
MARRIED ?

07:40.920 --> 07:42.182
WHEN ?

07:42.220 --> 07:43.687
DAY AFTER TOMORROW.

07:43.730 --> 07:47.951
A SMALL CEREMONY,
JUST ME AND GEORGE,

07:48.000 --> 07:49.228
AND ALL OF YOU.

07:49.260 --> 07:51.228
UH, YOU GUYS MET
LIKE, LAST WEEK.

07:51.270 --> 07:53.261
SIX AND A HALF
WEEKS AGO, ACTUALLY.

07:53.300 --> 07:54.836
MOM !

07:54.870 --> 07:56.269
WHEN EXACTLY WERE YOU
PLANNING ON TELLING US ?

07:56.300 --> 07:58.063
WE ONLY BOOKED THE WEDDING
CHAPEL LAST NIGHT !

07:58.110 --> 08:00.032
I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.

08:00.080 --> 08:02.071
NATE, I LOVE
YOUR MOTHER.

08:02.110 --> 08:03.975
AND SHE LOVES ME.

08:04.010 --> 08:07.173
YEAH, THAT'S JUST SO FUCKING
MOVING I CAN HARDLY STAND IT.

08:07.220 --> 08:11.543
FINE, DO WHATEVER YOU WANT,
WHAT DO I CARE ?

08:14.020 --> 08:15.556
( door slamming )

08:16.990 --> 08:19.151
MOM, MAYBE WITH LISA
AND EVERYTHING, YOU SHOULD--

08:19.190 --> 08:20.851
LIFE DOESN'T STOP,
ALRIGHT ?

08:20.900 --> 08:22.561
WE DIDN'T DIE.

08:22.600 --> 08:25.967
WE HAVE THIS
PRECIOUS GIFT OF LIFE

08:26.000 --> 08:27.797
AND IT'S SO
TERRIBLY FLEETING

08:27.840 --> 08:30.104
AND THAT IS PRECISELY WHY IT'S
IMPORTANT TO KEEP ON LIVING,

08:30.140 --> 08:32.574
TO NOT GIVE UP HOPE.

08:36.180 --> 08:38.148
FINE, DON'T COME.

08:38.180 --> 08:40.944
IF NO ONE'S GOING
TO CELEBRATE THIS WITH US,

08:40.980 --> 08:42.311
THEN I DON'T WANT
ANY OF YOU THERE.

08:42.350 --> 08:46.241
LET'S GO
BACK TO BED.

08:54.100 --> 08:56.022
IT'S UPSETTING TO YOU,

08:56.060 --> 08:57.322
THAT YOUR KIDS
DON'T APPROVE, ISN'T IT ?

08:57.370 --> 08:58.860
DO YOUR CHILDREN
APPROVE ?

08:58.900 --> 09:01.664
THEY'RE...

09:01.700 --> 09:03.668
SUPPORTIVE.

09:03.710 --> 09:05.905
BUT MAGGIE SAYS
TO JUST SEND PICTURES.

09:05.940 --> 09:07.828
AND BRIAN SAID SIX
AND HE'S DONE.

09:07.880 --> 09:10.804
I DON'T NEED
THEIR APPROVAL.

09:10.850 --> 09:16.243
NOT ONE OF THEM HAS EVER HAD
A RELATIONSHIP I'D WANT.

09:16.280 --> 09:18.339
GEORGE, I DON'T
WANT TO WAIT.

09:18.390 --> 09:22.759
I FEEL LIKE I'VE SPENT
MY ENTIRE LIFE WAITING.

09:22.790 --> 09:25.122
THEN LET'S NOT WAIT.

09:27.830 --> 09:29.593
THEY DON'T EVEN
KNOW EACH OTHER.

09:29.630 --> 09:32.599
ALTHOUGH, MAYBE THAT'S
THE BEST TIME TO MARRY SOMEONE.

09:32.640 --> 09:35.063
OTHERWISE,
YOU'D NEVER DO IT.

09:45.850 --> 09:49.013
HOW ARE YOU HOLDING UP
THROUGH ALL THIS ?

09:49.050 --> 09:52.213
NOT THAT GOOD.

09:52.250 --> 09:55.287
YOU WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT ?

09:55.320 --> 09:58.027
HOW CAN I ?

09:58.060 --> 10:02.292
WITH LISA JUST GONE, AND
NATE'S LIKE TOTALLY LOSING IT.

10:02.330 --> 10:06.369
I FEEL LIKE I DON'T REALLY HAVE
A RIGHT TO HAVE MY OWN PROBLEMS.

10:06.400 --> 10:09.699
OF COURSE
YOU HAVE A RIGHT.

10:11.940 --> 10:14.374
IS IT RUSSELL ?

10:14.410 --> 10:16.799
GOD, IT'S SO MUCH
MORE THAN THAT.

10:24.150 --> 10:29.679
A YEAR AGO, I WAS LIKE, IF I
CAN JUST GET INTO ART SCHOOL,

10:29.730 --> 10:32.119
THEN MAYBE, FINALLY,

10:32.160 --> 10:34.924
MY LIFE WILL START TO BE
ABOUT SOMETHING, YOU KNOW ?

10:34.960 --> 10:38.794
AND THEN I DO, AND IT'S JUST
SO SICKLY POLITICAL AND DUMB

10:38.830 --> 10:43.108
AND FULL OF EVIL,
HATEFUL FREAKS,

10:43.140 --> 10:48.669
THAT NOW I JUST DESPISE THE ONE
THING THAT WAS MY ONLY HOPE.

10:54.820 --> 10:57.687
AND YOUR WHOLE RELATIONSHIP
FELL APART TOO, HUH ?

10:57.720 --> 10:59.984
WELL, I WOULDN'T SAY--

11:00.020 --> 11:02.818
YEAH.

11:04.030 --> 11:06.021
SORRY.

11:06.060 --> 11:08.790
THAN KS.

11:17.070 --> 11:19.300
HEY, DON'T FORGET TO BRING
BACK YOUR COFFEE CUP.

11:21.110 --> 11:23.442
WE'RE RUNNING OUT OF
COFFEE CUPS IN THIS KITCHEN.

11:23.480 --> 11:28.019
PEOPLE KEEP
LEAVING WITH THEM.

11:42.230 --> 11:43.993
A PLANE !

11:44.030 --> 11:45.918
A PLANE GOING
TO BURBANK AIRPORT,

11:45.970 --> 11:47.392
JUST BEFORE LANDING.

11:47.440 --> 11:49.135
THEY CALL IT
THE BLUE ICE.

11:49.170 --> 11:50.808
I DON'T KNOW.

11:50.840 --> 11:54.230
SOME BALL OF CHEMICAL FOR TOILET
OF AIRPLANE IT COME OFF,

11:54.280 --> 11:56.430
RIGHT ONTO ANAHID.

11:56.480 --> 11:59.005
IN OUR OWN YARD.

11:59.050 --> 12:01.348
ONE MINUTE I'M TALKING TO HER
ON TELEPHONE, NEXT MINUTE.

12:01.380 --> 12:03.416
( speaking Armenian )

12:03.450 --> 12:05.486
YOU BELIEVE THIS ?

12:05.520 --> 12:08.216
AND NOW I FINDING OUT
IT'S HAPPEN ALL THE TIME,

12:08.260 --> 12:10.785
BUT BIG COMPANIES
THEY KEEPING IT QUIET

12:10.830 --> 12:12.081
SO PEOPLE LIKE ME
AND YOU DON'T REALIZE IT,

12:12.130 --> 12:14.496
THAT BLUE ICE
IS A KILLER !

12:17.500 --> 12:18.762
HEY.

12:18.800 --> 12:20.131
HEY.

12:20.170 --> 12:21.330
ARE YOU NOT
LISTENING TO ME ?

12:21.370 --> 12:23.201
ARE YOU HERE JUST
TO TAKE MY MONEY ?

12:23.240 --> 12:24.935
TH ESE PLACES !

12:24.970 --> 12:26.267
YOU TAKING FROM PEOPLE

12:26.310 --> 12:28.005
WHEN THEY'RE IN THEIR
MOST VULNERABLE !

12:28.040 --> 12:29.871
WHAT IS THIS, SOME KIND OF
A FUCKING BUSINESS TO YOU.

12:29.910 --> 12:32.003
GODDAMN RIGHT
IT'S A BUSINESS !

12:32.050 --> 12:33.449
WHAT DO YOU THINK I'M HERE FOR,
THE LOVE OF HUMANITY ?!

12:33.480 --> 12:35.414
YOU THINK
I WANT TO BE HERE,

12:35.450 --> 12:37.247
WITH PEOPLE ON THE WORST
FUCKING DAY OF THEIR LIVES ?!

12:37.290 --> 12:39.349
I WANT TO TALK
TO YOUR BOSS, PLEASE.

12:39.390 --> 12:41.119
I AM THE BOSS.

12:41.160 --> 12:43.025
AND I WANT YOU OUT OF
MY FUCKING ESTABLISHMENT, NOW !

12:45.090 --> 12:47.126
GO ON,
GET THE FUCK OUT !

12:47.160 --> 12:50.266
I'LL HAVE YOUR WIFE BROUGHT
OVER TO WHEREVER YOU END UP.

12:50.300 --> 12:52.393
FREE OF FUCKING CHARGE.

12:52.430 --> 12:54.569
JUST OUT OF THE GOODNESS
OF MY HEART,

12:54.600 --> 12:56.238
BECAUSE I'M IN THIS BUSINESS
BECAUSE I LOVE PEOPLE

12:56.270 --> 12:58.830
AND I LOVE
HELPING PEOPLE !

13:00.480 --> 13:02.334
I FELT SO FREE.

13:02.380 --> 13:03.574
YOU KNOW,
FOR LIKE A WEEK.

13:03.610 --> 13:05.202
BUT THEN ALL OF A SUDDEN,
WITHIN DAYS,

13:05.250 --> 13:06.877
IT WENT FROM YAY,
I'M INDEPENDENT

13:06.920 --> 13:08.376
TO HOLY FUCK,
I'M GOING TO DIE ALONE.

13:08.420 --> 13:11.344
I KEEP SWITCHING BACK
AND FORTH BETWEEN, YOU KNOW,

13:11.390 --> 13:14.018
WE'RE MEANT TO BE TOGETHER,
WE CAN GROW TOGETHER,

13:14.060 --> 13:16.449
INTO WHO WE FULLY ARE, TOGETHER,
YOU KNOW WHATI MEAN ?

13:16.490 --> 13:18.082
NOT REALLY.

13:18.130 --> 13:20.291
AND THEN ALL OF A SUDDEN
I COMPLETELY FLIP OVER

13:20.330 --> 13:22.195
TO WE'RE POISON FOR
EACH OTHER, THIS IS ABUSE.

13:22.230 --> 13:26.929
YOU ALWAYS GO THROUGH
TOUGH PATCHES, DAVID.

13:26.970 --> 13:29.165
YOU JUST HAVE
TO WORK THROUGH THEM.

13:29.200 --> 13:31.031
HAVE YOU AND VANESSA
EVER GONE THROUGH A TIME

13:31.070 --> 13:32.901
WHERE YOU FELT LIKE
BY STAYING WITH HER

13:32.940 --> 13:35.238
YOUR ENTIRE SENSE OF SELF
WAS GOING TO BE OBLITERATED ?

13:35.280 --> 13:37.248
UH...

13:37.280 --> 13:38.474
NO.

13:38.510 --> 13:39.841
I DIDN'T THINK SO.

13:39.880 --> 13:42.178
VANESSA AND I
HAVE OUR ISSUES,

13:42.220 --> 13:46.543
MAINLY BECAUSE OTHER PEOPLE
TRY TO COME BETWEEN US.

13:46.590 --> 13:48.615
WOULD THAT BE
ANGELICA ?

13:48.660 --> 13:52.426
I SWEAR, DAVID.

13:52.460 --> 13:54.849
I WISH I COULD JUST
KICK HER SORRY ASS OUT.

13:54.900 --> 13:57.095
THEN VAN ESSA ALWAYS
TAKES HER SIDE,

13:57.130 --> 13:59.098
IT'S LIKE I HAVE
A FUCKING TWO-HEADED WIFE.

13:59.130 --> 14:01.337
AS OPPOSED
TO A NO-HEADED WIFE.

14:01.370 --> 14:03.565
THAT'S GOOD.

14:03.610 --> 14:05.362
UNHOOK HER !
EXCUSE ME ?

14:05.410 --> 14:06.308
JUST FUCKING
UNHOOK HER !

14:06.340 --> 14:07.602
WHOA, WHOA, HEY !

14:07.640 --> 14:08.868
WHAT IS WRONG
WITH YOU ?

14:08.910 --> 14:11.071
THE HUSBAND
CHANGED HIS MIND.

14:11.110 --> 14:13.510
OKAY, BUT WAIT UNTIL I GET
THE CANULA OUT OF HER.

14:13.550 --> 14:14.949
AND I SHOULD REALLY
ASPIRATE BEFORE WE MOVE HER.

14:14.980 --> 14:16.880
DID WE GET
OUTBID AGAIN ?

14:16.920 --> 14:20.959
YEAH, THE PRIEST OR PASTOR
OR WHATEVER FROM THEIR CHURCH

14:20.990 --> 14:23.379
WANTED TO USE A DIFFERENT PLACE,
AN ARMENIAN PLACE.

14:23.430 --> 14:25.159
IT'S NO BIG DEAL.

14:25.190 --> 14:26.896
WELL, MAKE SURE WE CHARGE THEM
EXTRA FOR EMBALMING AND TRANSPO.

14:26.930 --> 14:30.127
I TOLD THEM
IT WOULD BE FREE.

14:30.170 --> 14:31.489
WHY DID YOU
DO THAT ?!

14:31.530 --> 14:34.192
YOU JUST LOST US
$500, NATE !

14:34.240 --> 14:35.969
BECAUSE I MADE
A MISTAKE, ALRIGHT ?

14:36.000 --> 14:38.059
YEAH, I MADE
A FUCKING MISTAKE !

14:38.110 --> 14:39.975
YOU WANT TO TAKE IT OUT
OF MY FUCKIN' PAYCHECK ?!

14:40.010 --> 14:42.478
FUCK YOU GUYS !

14:45.280 --> 14:47.168
I'm so alone.

14:47.220 --> 14:49.279
You're not alone.

14:49.320 --> 14:50.446
You have me.

14:50.490 --> 14:53.311
Do I, Philip ?

14:53.360 --> 14:55.920
Do I really ?

14:58.160 --> 15:00.151
How can I ever trust you after
what happened in Budapest ?

15:00.200 --> 15:02.088
I had amnesia,
I'd been brainwashed !

15:02.130 --> 15:03.620
HEY.

15:03.670 --> 15:05.092
I NEED YOU
TO WATCH MAYA FOR ME.

15:05.130 --> 15:06.165
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

15:06.200 --> 15:07.690
NATE, I WANT
TO HELP YOU,

15:07.740 --> 15:11.198
I CAN'T IMAGINE WHAT YOU'RE
DEALING WITH BUT I AM SERIOUSLY,

15:11.240 --> 15:13.276
AS OUT OF IT AS
YOU ARE RIGHT NOW.

15:13.310 --> 15:14.572
I DON'T THINK MY ENERGY
WOULD BE VERY GOOD FOR MAYA.

15:14.610 --> 15:16.271
YOU'RE BETTER
THAN ME.

15:21.750 --> 15:23.388
Well, maybe when it
comes to forgiving,

15:23.420 --> 15:25.980
you need to start
with yourself.

15:27.460 --> 15:30.679
( music )

15:49.580 --> 15:51.377
ONE MORE ?

15:51.410 --> 15:54.573
YEAH, DO YOU GUYS
SELL ANY FOOD HERE ?

15:54.620 --> 15:56.645
PEAN UTS.

15:56.680 --> 15:58.181
THEM EGGS
OVER THERE.

15:58.220 --> 16:00.711
I COULD
ORDER YOU A PIZZA.

16:00.760 --> 16:04.184
NO, I CAN'T EAT
A WHOLE PIZZA.

16:10.500 --> 16:13.094
I'LL HAVE
A SLICE WITH YOU.

16:15.370 --> 16:17.008
HAWAIIAN ?

16:17.040 --> 16:19.167
HAM AND PINEAPPLE ?

16:19.210 --> 16:25.274
SORRY, I'M NOT A PINEAPPLE
ON PIZZA KIND OF GUY.

16:25.310 --> 16:27.016
OH YEAH ?

16:27.050 --> 16:30.144
WHAT KINDA
A GUY ARE YA ?

16:33.160 --> 16:35.617
THE KIND OF GUY WHO WANTS
TO FUCK YOU SENSELESS.

16:47.440 --> 16:51.399
( French horn playing )

17:06.520 --> 17:07.509
AM I TOO LOUD ?

17:07.560 --> 17:08.811
OH, NO.

17:08.860 --> 17:10.350
I WAS JUST CURIOUS
WHAT THE SOUND WAS.

17:10.390 --> 17:11.755
FRENCH HORN.

17:11.790 --> 17:13.826
NOBODY EVER KNOWS
WHAT IT IS.

17:13.860 --> 17:15.293
IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

17:15.330 --> 17:16.524
DON'T LIE,
THERE'S NO NEED.

17:16.560 --> 17:19.620
IT'S NOT ONE OF
THOSE INSTRUMENTS

17:19.670 --> 17:21.467
THAT'S MEANT
TO BE HEARD ALONE.

17:21.500 --> 17:24.264
OH, I'M BRENDA.

17:25.340 --> 17:26.307
JOE.

17:26.340 --> 17:27.637
HEY.
HEY.

17:27.680 --> 17:29.705
I JUST MOVED IN
A MONTH AND A HALF AGO.

17:29.740 --> 17:32.140
OH, WELCOME.

17:32.180 --> 17:33.738
I'VE BEEN HERE FOR
ABOUT EIGHT YEARS.

17:33.780 --> 17:36.146
SEEMS LIKE
A NICE ENOUGH PLACE.

17:36.180 --> 17:38.284
YEAH, I LIKE IT.

17:38.320 --> 17:41.153
PLUS, IT'S CHEAP SO
I DON'T HAVE TO WORK A LOT.

17:41.190 --> 17:44.728
I DO SESSION WORK MOSTLY,
BUT THESE DAYS MOST PEOPLE

17:44.760 --> 17:49.151
PREFER THE SYNTHESIZED
PSEUDO-HORN BY-PRODUCT
OF THAT OF AN ACTUAL HUMAN.

17:49.200 --> 17:50.724
DO I SOUND ANGRY ?

17:50.770 --> 17:51.794
'CAUSE I'M NOT ANGRY.

17:51.830 --> 17:54.162
NO, IT'S FINE,
IT'S NICE...

17:54.200 --> 17:55.531
TO TALK TO SOMEONE.

17:55.570 --> 17:58.368
JUST GET OUT OF PRISON ?

17:58.410 --> 18:00.105
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

18:00.140 --> 18:03.644
HAVE YOU FULLY CHECKED OUT
THE NEIGHBORHOOD YET ?

18:03.680 --> 18:05.102
FIGURED OUT
WHERE STUFF IS ?

18:05.150 --> 18:06.208
NAH.

18:06.250 --> 18:07.842
NAH ?

