36:23.810 --> 36:25.869
OKAY, LOOK.

36:25.910 --> 36:27.605
LISTEN TO ME.

36:27.650 --> 36:29.311
I LOVE YOU
WITH ALL MY HEART.

36:29.350 --> 36:32.217
AND I'LL DO ANYTHING I HAVE
TO DO TO WORK THROUGH THIS,

36:32.250 --> 36:34.457
BECAUSE I DON'T
WANT TO LOSE YOU.

36:44.370 --> 36:45.928
I CAN'T PROMISE YOU
ANYTHING.

36:45.970 --> 36:48.632
JUST DON'T GIVE UP.

36:48.670 --> 36:51.969
NOT YET.

37:03.980 --> 37:05.641
WHERE ARE YOU GOING ?

37:05.690 --> 37:07.544
I DON'T WANNA SIT AROUND
LIKE A PIG IN MY OWN FILTH

37:07.590 --> 37:09.751
FOR ONE SUNDAY
IF NOBODY MINDS.

37:09.790 --> 37:12.759
HEY, SWEETIE.

37:12.790 --> 37:14.792
WHY DON'T WE
GO TO CHURCH ?

37:14.830 --> 37:16.422
WHY DON'T WE
DO SOMETHING ?

37:16.460 --> 37:18.826
OH BABY, ANGIE JUST RENTED
THE KIDS A BUNCH OF MOVIES.

37:20.370 --> 37:21.632
WHOA.

37:21.670 --> 37:23.934
WHOA, ANGIE, HEY,
THAT'S NOT FOR KIDS.

37:23.970 --> 37:25.267
PUT ON SOMETHING ELSE.

37:25.310 --> 37:26.607
WHAT THEY GET,
THEY GET,

37:26.640 --> 37:27.766
WHAT THEY DON'T GET
GOES OVER THEIR HEADS ANYWAY

37:27.810 --> 37:29.004
SO, DON'T EVEN
STRESS ABOUT IT.

37:29.040 --> 37:30.302
THAT DOESN'T
MAKE ANY SENSE.

37:30.340 --> 37:31.477
IT MAKES PERFECT SENSE.

37:31.510 --> 37:33.000
I HAVE TO GO
TO THE POTTY.

37:33.050 --> 37:35.268
WILL YOU PUT IT
ON PAUSE ?

37:37.450 --> 37:38.439
HEY!

37:38.490 --> 37:39.548
THAT'S MY SHIRT !

37:39.590 --> 37:41.854
SORRY, I JUST
SLEPT IN IT.

37:41.890 --> 37:43.209
I'LL WASH IT.

37:47.090 --> 37:48.591
THAT'S IT.

37:48.630 --> 37:50.393
THAT IS IT,
THAT'S IT !

37:50.430 --> 37:51.692
YOUR SISTER HAS GOT
TO GO FOR GOOD.

37:51.730 --> 37:53.061
SHE'S BEEN LOOKING
IN THE ADS.

37:53.100 --> 37:54.761
SHE NEEDS TO FIND
A ROOMMATE FIRST !

37:54.800 --> 37:56.665
SHE'S BEEN PUTTING IT OFF,
SHE HASN'T BEEN LOOKING.

37:56.700 --> 37:57.837
WHY SHOULD SHE ?

37:57.870 --> 37:59.007
SHE'S IN HOG HEAVEN
OVER HERE.

37:59.040 --> 38:00.735
RICO, THAT IS
MY SISTER !

38:00.770 --> 38:02.328
AND I AM
YOUR HUSBAND !

38:02.380 --> 38:03.335
WE WOULDN'T EVEN BE
IN THIS HOUSE

38:03.380 --> 38:04.506
IF IT WEREN'T
FOR HER !

38:04.550 --> 38:06.802
WE PAID HER
THAT MONEY BACK !

38:06.850 --> 38:08.772
LOOK, WE NEEDED HELP,
SHE WAS THERE.

38:08.820 --> 38:10.412
NOW SHE NEEDS HELP !

38:12.020 --> 38:13.544
RICO !

38:13.590 --> 38:15.911
RICO !

38:15.960 --> 38:17.689
RICO, YOU BETTER NOT
SLAM THAT DOOR--

38:17.720 --> 38:18.982
( door slamming )

38:25.030 --> 38:27.419
I'LL WAIT
FOR YOU OUT HERE.

38:27.470 --> 38:29.438
YOU'RE NOT ALLOWED
TO SMOKE IN THERE.

38:48.960 --> 38:51.554
CLAIRE !

38:54.660 --> 38:56.799
OH MY GOD.

38:58.500 --> 39:00.798
PLEASE TELL ME
YOU'RE JUST VISITING.

39:00.830 --> 39:01.933
YEAH.

39:01.970 --> 39:03.369
YEAH.

39:03.400 --> 39:05.800
SO YOU'RE--

39:05.840 --> 39:07.398
COULDN'T BE BETTER.

39:07.440 --> 39:09.829
OKAY, I AM SO
NOT GETTING THIS.

39:09.880 --> 39:11.973
THERE'S NOTHING TO GET.

39:12.010 --> 39:15.138
LISA, IF I'D KNOWN
YOU WERE GONNA DIE,

39:15.180 --> 39:17.114
I WOULD HAVE HUNG OUT
WITH YOU MORE.

39:17.150 --> 39:20.085
OH, YOU'RE SO SWEET.

39:30.830 --> 39:33.162
ISN'T HE BEAUTIFUL ?

39:33.200 --> 39:36.499
DON'T WORRY, I'LL TAKE
GOOD CARE OF HIM.

39:36.540 --> 39:41.671
AND YOU TAKE CARE
OF MAYA FOR ME, OKAY ?

39:53.850 --> 39:55.818
YOU KNOW I MISS YOU
AND I THINK ABOUT YOU,

39:55.860 --> 39:56.918
LIKE ALL THE TIME.

39:56.960 --> 40:00.589
RIGHT BACK AT YOU.

40:00.630 --> 40:04.623
IT'S SO WEIRD THAT
MOM'S GETTING MARRIED.

40:04.670 --> 40:07.059
IT'S LIKE...

40:07.100 --> 40:08.965
I DON'T KNOW, IT'S LIKE YOU'RE
BEING ERASED OR SOMETHING.

40:09.000 --> 40:09.932
AREN'T YOU
PISSED OFF ?

40:09.970 --> 40:11.528
NAH, THAT'S YOU.

40:11.570 --> 40:14.676
I THINK THIS IS WHAT
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR.

40:29.960 --> 40:34.499
( phone ringing )

40:44.940 --> 40:45.964
YEAH ?

40:46.010 --> 40:47.568
( male )
Mr. Fisher ?

40:47.610 --> 40:48.929
YEAH.

40:48.980 --> 40:50.675
This is
Deputy Wheeler

40:50.710 --> 40:52.678
from the Santa Barbara
Sheriff's Department.

40:52.710 --> 40:55.213
I'm afraid I've got
some bad news for you, Sir,

40:55.250 --> 40:58.708
you might want
to sit down.

41:04.060 --> 41:05.948
OKAY.

41:05.990 --> 41:08.652
We found
a body, sir,

41:08.700 --> 41:13.728
and it matches with
your wife's dental records.

41:13.770 --> 41:16.466
I'm so sorry.

41:18.570 --> 41:21.107
( Latin music playing )

41:31.180 --> 41:33.216
YOU READ ALL THESE
ARTICLES, YOU KNOW,

41:33.250 --> 41:37.118
HOW AUSTIN'S SUPPOSED TO BE THIS
HIP, HOT ENCLAVE OF ARTISTS,

41:37.160 --> 41:38.752
BUT GOD, IT WAS
MORE THAN JUST HOT.

41:38.790 --> 41:41.520
A MILLION DEGREES
AT ALL TIMES.

41:41.560 --> 41:44.199
I'D BE LAYING AROUND
MY APARTMENT GOING,

41:44.230 --> 41:47.620
"I KNOW I NEED TO EXPERIENCE
THAT EDGY LOCAL SONGWRITER

41:47.670 --> 41:49.831
"WHO'S PLAYING AT
THE FABULOUS NEW CLUB

41:49.870 --> 41:52.259
BUT I'M JUST
SO DAMN HOT."

41:52.310 --> 41:53.902
IS THAT WHY YOU
CAME BACK TO L.A. ?

41:53.940 --> 41:55.703
MY DAD GOT SICK.

41:55.740 --> 41:57.037
OH, I'M SORRY.

41:57.080 --> 41:59.969
HE DIED, ACTUALLY.

42:00.010 --> 42:02.114
OH, I'M REALLY SORRY.

42:02.150 --> 42:04.243
OH THANK YOU,
IT'S OKAY.

42:04.280 --> 42:08.910
THE ODDEST PART IS THAT
I ACTUALLY RETURNED

42:08.960 --> 42:11.827
WITH THE INTENTION OF
RECONNECTING WITH MY FAMILY.

42:11.860 --> 42:14.249
AND THEN, WITHIN
A MATTER OF MONTHS,

42:14.290 --> 42:16.895
I'M IN THIS
PLACE WHERE...

42:16.930 --> 42:20.320
WITHOUT SAYING TOO MUCH
AGAIN AND SCARING YOU.

42:20.370 --> 42:23.259
SAY WHATEVER YOU WANT.

42:24.810 --> 42:28.837
I... I ACTUALLY
HAVE NO ONE.

42:28.880 --> 42:31.804
I DON'T THINK
I'VE EVER BEEN SO...

42:31.850 --> 42:35.274
BY MYSELF.

42:46.190 --> 42:48.055
I KNOW THAT ONE DAY
I NEED TO START--

42:48.090 --> 42:50.650
I WANT TO START
DATING AGAIN.

42:50.700 --> 42:53.828
FUCK DATING,
DATING IS STUPID.

42:53.870 --> 42:56.088
( laughing )

42:56.140 --> 43:00.008
BUT THIS IS A DATE.

43:00.040 --> 43:01.302
ISN'T IT, KIND OF ?

43:01.340 --> 43:03.376
WELL, IT IS IF
WE WANT IT TO BE.

43:03.410 --> 43:07.176
DO YOU WANT IT TO BE ?

43:08.410 --> 43:11.117
CAN I GET BACK
TO YOU ON THAT ?

43:11.150 --> 43:13.311
TAKE YOUR TIME.

43:22.100 --> 43:25.126
I KNOW THE WOMAN THAT
TEACHES SALSA ON TUESDAYS.

43:25.170 --> 43:27.161
SHE'S DELIGHTFUL.

43:27.200 --> 43:28.929
I'LL CHECK IT OUT.

43:28.970 --> 43:30.096
I'M TAKING OFF.

43:30.140 --> 43:31.960
OKAY.

43:32.010 --> 43:34.308
I THINK THEY'RE USING THIS SPACE
FOR A PRIVATE PARTY TONIGHT,

43:34.340 --> 43:36.035
WE PROBABLY
SHOULD CLEAR OUT.

43:36.080 --> 43:38.776
OH, OKAY.

43:41.410 --> 43:43.116
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO GET A DRINK ?

43:43.150 --> 43:44.742
YOU LOOK LIKE
YOU HAVE SOME TIME.

43:44.790 --> 43:46.246
OH, MAN, I'VE GOT
NOTHING BUT TIME.

43:46.290 --> 43:48.110
THANK YOU.

43:48.150 --> 43:49.219
WHERE'S YOUR CAR ?

43:49.260 --> 43:50.386
IN THE LOT.

43:50.420 --> 43:51.819
WHY DON'T YOU
FOLLOW ME ?

43:51.860 --> 43:53.020
OKAY.

43:53.060 --> 43:55.722
* YOU AIN'T GOT
NO WORRY *

44:09.910 --> 44:12.071
SO, WHAT'LL IT BE ?

44:12.110 --> 44:15.409
A SHOT OF TEQUILA.

44:15.450 --> 44:18.374
( Nate )
YOU WANT TO GET TO YOUR
SISTER'S BEFORE DARK, RIGHT ?

44:18.420 --> 44:20.638
YOU WANT
TO GET RID OF ME.

44:24.190 --> 44:26.658
KEEP IT COMING.

44:52.120 --> 44:53.109
HI, MOM.

44:53.150 --> 44:54.481
HELLO, DEAR.

44:54.520 --> 44:57.080
YOU LOOK BEAUTIFUL.

44:59.490 --> 45:02.152
HOW LONG BEFORE
WE LEAVE ?

45:02.200 --> 45:05.795
A COUPLE OF HOURS.

45:05.830 --> 45:07.320
OH GOOD.

45:07.370 --> 45:09.258
I WAS AFRAID
I WAS GONNA BE LATE.

45:09.300 --> 45:13.361
DO YOU WANT ME TO PACK UP
THE VIDEO CAMERA ?

45:13.410 --> 45:15.833
NO, THEY PROVIDE THAT
AT THE CHAPEL.

45:15.880 --> 45:19.202
BUT MAYBE YOU COULD
TAKE CARE OF MAYA TONIGHT,

45:19.250 --> 45:20.274
AT THE WEDDING ?

45:20.310 --> 45:22.278
GEORGE HAS HER
RIGHT NOW.

45:22.320 --> 45:25.118
WHERE'S NATE ?

45:25.150 --> 45:27.186
I HAVE NO IDEA.

45:27.220 --> 45:30.849
I'VE TRIED CALLING
HIS CELL PHONE ALL AFTERNOON

45:30.890 --> 45:33.029
BUT THERE'S NO ANSWER.

45:37.830 --> 45:40.867
OH, I HAVE
SOMETHING FOR YOU.

45:49.440 --> 45:51.943
THEY'RE ANTIQUE,
SO THEY'RE OLD,

45:51.980 --> 45:53.845
BUT I JUST BOUGHT THEM,
SO THEY'RE ALSO NEW.

45:53.880 --> 45:56.246
AND TECH NICALLY
I'M GIVING THEM TO YOU,

45:56.280 --> 45:57.941
RATHER THAN LETTING YOU
BORROW THEM, BUT.

45:57.980 --> 46:00.949
THEY'RE BLUE, RIGHT ?

46:03.320 --> 46:05.049
I LOVE YOU, MOM.

46:05.090 --> 46:07.354
I'M SO HAPPY THAT YOU
FOUND YOUR SOUL-MATE.

46:07.390 --> 46:11.326
THANK YOU, MY SWEET
DARLING CLAIRE.

46:11.360 --> 46:15.467
YOU DON'T KNOW HOW MUCH
THIS MEANS TO ME...

46:15.500 --> 46:17.889
FROM YOU.

46:26.280 --> 46:28.271
DO YOU LIKE THEM ?

46:28.310 --> 46:29.538
THEY'RE BEAUTIFUL.

46:29.580 --> 46:33.209
PRETTY.

46:33.250 --> 46:36.287
( music )

46:46.430 --> 46:49.228
NOTHING TO WORRY ABOUT, KID,
JUST A PLACE TO GET A DRINK.

46:49.270 --> 46:51.534
I KNOW, I KNOW,
I JUST...

46:51.570 --> 46:53.367
I JUST NORMALLY
DON'T DO THIS.

46:53.410 --> 46:57.835
THESE LADIES,
THEY'RE VERY NICE.

47:20.270 --> 47:23.137
( cheering )

47:26.640 --> 47:28.608
SO...

47:35.480 --> 47:38.142
THAT WASN'T A KISS.

47:38.180 --> 47:40.080
NO.

47:40.120 --> 47:43.112
BUT IT WAS CLOSE.

47:51.300 --> 47:52.619
GOODNIGHT.

47:52.670 --> 47:54.467
GOODNIGHT.

48:11.350 --> 48:13.409
HI.

48:13.450 --> 48:15.384
OH, HEY.

48:15.420 --> 48:17.479
I'M INFINITY.

48:17.520 --> 48:19.954
HI, I'M RICO.

48:19.990 --> 48:21.628
HI.

48:21.660 --> 48:24.026
THIS IS A GREAT SONG !

48:24.060 --> 48:27.496
YEAH, WHEN ARE YOU
GONNA DANCE AGAIN ?

48:27.530 --> 48:29.464
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
A GREAT DANCER.

48:29.500 --> 48:31.491
SOON, DON'T WORRY.

48:31.540 --> 48:34.566
MY REAL NAME
IS SOPHIA.

48:34.610 --> 48:37.272
BUT YOU GOT
TO CALL ME INFINITY.

48:37.310 --> 48:39.346
HOW COME ?

48:39.380 --> 48:41.200
I DON'T KNOW,
IT'S THE RULES.

48:41.250 --> 48:45.949
I'M SORRY, I'VE JUST NEVER BEEN
TO A PLACE LIKE THIS BEFORE.

48:45.990 --> 48:47.480
( laughing )

48:47.520 --> 48:50.489
DUH !

48:55.530 --> 48:59.318
WHEN ARE YOU
GONNA DANCE AGAIN ?

48:59.370 --> 49:02.032
( laughing )

49:18.680 --> 49:21.979
COULD YOU PLEASE
STOP DOING THAT ?

49:23.590 --> 49:26.320
IF YOU CAN GIVE ME
A GOOD REASON TO.

49:26.360 --> 49:28.555
BECAUSE IT'S DRIVING ME
FUCKING CRAZY.

49:28.590 --> 49:32.128
NOT A GOOD
ENOUGH REASON.

49:45.180 --> 49:47.740
WHAT THE FUCK IS
YOUR PROBLEM, ASSHOLE ?

49:47.780 --> 49:50.146
YOU'RE MY PROBLEM,
YOU DUMB PIECE OF SHIT.

49:51.820 --> 49:55.415
HOW'S YOUR PROBLEM NOW,
ASSHOLE ?

49:57.360 --> 49:58.657
DON'T YOU CALL ME
A FUCKING PIECE OF SHIT.

49:58.690 --> 50:00.988
ASSHOLE !

50:14.370 --> 50:15.735
COME ON.

50:15.780 --> 50:17.475
COME ON, DO IT.

50:17.510 --> 50:18.704
DO IT.

50:18.740 --> 50:21.573
COME ON,
YOU FUCKING DIPSHIT.

50:21.610 --> 50:23.168
I CAN STILL
FUCKING STAND UP !

50:23.220 --> 50:25.142
COME ON !

50:25.190 --> 50:27.647
COME ON, FINISH
WHAT YOU STARTED !

50:27.690 --> 50:30.284
COME ON !

50:30.320 --> 50:31.651
FIGHT,
YOU FUCKING PUSSY !

50:31.690 --> 50:33.385
COME ON !

50:33.430 --> 50:36.251
I STAND BEFORE YOU WITH ONLY
MYSELF AND MY TIME TO GIVE.

50:36.300 --> 50:40.066
I WANT TO BE WITH YOU
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

50:40.100 --> 50:42.261
TO SEE JOY
THROUGH YOUR EYES,

50:42.300 --> 50:45.167
TO FEEL SORROW
THROUGH YOUR HEART,

50:45.210 --> 50:49.078
TO SHARE ALL THE WONDERS
OF EXISTENCE WITH YOU,

50:49.110 --> 50:51.328
DEAREST RUTH,

50:51.380 --> 50:54.838
AS MY CONSTANT
COMPANION,

50:54.880 --> 50:57.348
LOVE R,

50:57.380 --> 50:59.712
FRIEND.

51:04.120 --> 51:06.122
GEORGE, I HAVE
FUN WITH YOU.

51:06.160 --> 51:10.153
I WANT TO BELONG
TO YOU, MY DARLING.

51:10.200 --> 51:11.690
I WANT TO BE YOURS.

51:11.730 --> 51:13.527
AND SO--

51:13.570 --> 51:18.166
( sobbing )

51:22.240 --> 51:28.406
TODAY, I PROMISE MYSELF
TO YOU, FOREVER.

51:28.450 --> 51:31.214
I'M SORRY.

51:31.250 --> 51:33.684
I NOW PRONOUNCE YOU
MAN AND WIFE.

51:38.490 --> 51:41.152
( sobbing )

51:54.810 --> 51:56.801
OH.

52:00.710 --> 52:02.849
OH MY GOD.

52:02.880 --> 52:07.488
JEEZ.

52:07.520 --> 52:10.648
OH MY GOD.

52:12.830 --> 52:16.322
OH MAN.

52:16.360 --> 52:18.920
HOW MUCH DO
I OWE YOU ?

52:18.960 --> 52:22.259
WHAT ARE YOU CRAZY ?

52:22.300 --> 52:24.666
I'M NOT
A PROSTITUTE !

52:24.700 --> 52:26.361
OH, I'M SO SORRY.

52:26.410 --> 52:28.503
I'M SO SORRY,
I THOUGHT--

52:28.540 --> 52:30.371
SHIT.

52:30.410 --> 52:32.844
I DIDN'T MEAN IT ABOUT YOU,
I MEANT IT ABOUT ME,

52:32.880 --> 52:35.178
I DON'T KNOW
HOW PEOPLE--

52:35.220 --> 52:38.849
CUTIE, DON'T YOU KNOW,

52:38.880 --> 52:41.383
I WANNA BE YOUR FRIEND.

52:41.420 --> 52:43.217
I LIKE YOU,
DUM-DUM.

52:43.260 --> 52:45.478
OH.

52:51.660 --> 52:53.321
SO, UH...

52:53.370 --> 52:56.965
IS THERE ANY PLACE THAT
YOU WANT ME TO TAKE YOU ?

52:57.000 --> 53:02.336
BECAUSE I'M DONE,
IF THAT'S OKAY.

53:14.990 --> 53:17.709
* CAME IN LAST NIGHT
AT HALF PAST 10 *

53:17.760 --> 53:20.649
* THAT BABY OF MINE
WOULDN'T LET ME IN *

53:20.690 --> 53:22.590
* SO, I'M MOVIN' ON OVER

53:22.630 --> 53:25.326
* MOVIN' ON OVER,
MOVIN' ON OVER *

53:25.370 --> 53:30.364
* MOVE ON LITTLE DOG,
'CAUSE THE BIG DOG'S MOVIN' IN *

53:32.970 --> 53:34.562
HELLO, DAVID.

53:34.610 --> 53:35.508
KEITH.

53:35.540 --> 53:38.532
53;};

53:38.580 --> 53:40.502
CONGRATULATIONS
ON THE JOYOUS EVENT.

53:40.550 --> 53:43.747
THAT'S A GIFT
THAT I BOUGHT...

53:43.780 --> 53:46.783
FOR THEM.

53:46.820 --> 53:50.415
AW, THAT'S SO NICE.

53:50.460 --> 53:51.688
HERE, HAVE SOME CAKE.

53:51.720 --> 53:55.554
I DIDN'T WANT
TO HELP MYSELF.

53:55.600 --> 53:56.453
PLEASE.

53:56.500 --> 53:57.649
HERE.

53:57.700 --> 53:59.895
THAN KS.

53:59.930 --> 54:03.764
( Ruth laughing )

54:15.580 --> 54:17.047
IF NO ONE MINDS,

54:17.080 --> 54:19.287
I THINK I'LL ENJOY
THIS IN MY ROOM.

54:19.320 --> 54:20.719
OF COURSE.

54:20.750 --> 54:22.581
GOODNIGHT.

54:22.620 --> 54:24.281
GOODNIGHT.

54:31.000 --> 54:32.968
SAD GUY, HUH ?

54:33.000 --> 54:34.592
MMM.

54:38.500 --> 54:40.764
I MEAN, YOU WERE BORN
INTO THIS BUSINESS,

54:40.810 --> 54:41.959
HE ACTUALLY
CHOSE IT.

54:42.010 --> 54:45.878
SEE, YOU'RE PICKING
ON ME AGAIN.

54:45.910 --> 54:47.844
I WAS NOT,
I WAS PICKING ON HIM.

54:47.880 --> 54:48.904
AND ME, ADJACENTLY.

54:48.950 --> 54:50.645
ADJACENTLY
IS NOT A WORD.

54:50.680 --> 54:51.840
SEE, THAT'S PICKING.

54:51.880 --> 54:53.347
I WAS NOT PICKING,
I WAS TEASING.

54:53.390 --> 54:55.017
IT'S MY STYLE.

54:55.050 --> 54:56.756
YOU'RE PICKING
ON MY STYLE.

54:57.890 --> 55:00.927
( laughing )

55:08.770 --> 55:10.692
THIS CAKE'S
PRETTY GOOD.

55:10.740 --> 55:12.628
NOT REALLY.

55:15.880 --> 55:18.531
* SHE'LL CRAWL BACK TO ME
ON HER KNEES *

55:18.580 --> 55:21.845
* I'LL BE BUSY
SCRATCHING FLEES *

55:21.880 --> 55:24.644
* GO SLIDE IT ON OVER,
MOVE IT ON OVER *

55:24.680 --> 55:27.843
* SNEAK IT ON OVER,
MOVE IT ON OVER *

55:29.990 --> 55:31.912
MAKE A RIGHT
UP AHEAD.

55:31.960 --> 55:34.451
GO STRAIGHT UP
TO THE FIVE NORTH.

55:34.490 --> 55:36.629
THERE'S A PART THAT GOES
RIGHT OVER THE CANYON.

55:36.660 --> 55:37.752
THE GUARD RAIL'S OUT.

55:37.800 --> 55:39.597
AND YOU CAN
HURL YOURSELF

55:39.630 --> 55:40.927
AND THE CAR
AND YOUR LIFE RIGHT OVER.

55:40.970 --> 55:42.028
FUCK YOU.

55:42.070 --> 55:42.889
WHAT ARE YOU
WAITING FOR, HUH ?

55:42.940 --> 55:44.464
QUIT GRANDSTANDING.

55:44.500 --> 55:45.535
DO IT, DO IT !

55:45.570 --> 55:46.366
SHUT UP !

55:46.410 --> 55:47.900
SHUT THE FUCK UP !

55:47.940 --> 55:49.134
OK AT YOU,
YOU'RE SUCH A MESS.

55:49.170 --> 55:51.070
YOU'LL TAKE ANYONE,

55:51.110 --> 55:52.600
AS LONG AS THEY'LL
FUCK YOU OR FIGHT YOU.

